    "description": "Eiken Industries Co.,Ltd. engages in the manufacture and sale of filters for internal combustion engines and special filters for industrial use in Japan. It offers oil, air, fuel, air conditioner, and cabin filter. The company also provides kitchen equipment part; bunsen, infrared, ceramic, and blast burner; filters for water filtration and dust collectors; and heat exchanger, garage sauna, and household goods. In addition, it offers various filter elements for internal combustion engines of automobiles, construction machinery, and agricultural machinery, special filters for industrial machinery and other industrial applications. The company was formerly known as Ehken Kogyo Corporation and changed its name to Eiken Industries Co.,Ltd. in July 1972. Eiken Industries Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1967 and is headquartered in Omaezaki, Japan."
